snippet.title: VoxSys - Official Gameplay Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Put your skills to the test in frantic arena shooter, VoxSys. This new gameplay trailer gives us a look at the game's full destructible sci-fi maps as well as some of its powerful futuristic weapons. VoxSys is coming to Meta Quest, OpenXR, and PC. It's currently in Early Access on Steam.

#SummerOfGaming
